item.title: Week 2: Omek
item.description: [[2024-01-07-week-1|last week]] [[Freedom Is A Constant Struggle (2015)|Freedom Is A Constant Struggle (2015)]] [[Freedom Is A Constant|Freedom Is A Constant]] This week marked the week I got back into the swing of things at work. I tend to find the holiday season quite boring because things slow down quite a bit. Now that people are returning from their winter break, my to do list is filling up again with exciting projects, opportunities for collaboration, and research endeavors.
